<p>Last Wednesday, DailyMail.com also revealed that Vitolo broke it off with his live-in fiancée Rachel Emmons, 24, via text when handsy photos of him and Holmes were first published, leaving the handbag designer shocked and forcing her to move back home.</p>

<p>Katie and Emilio's friendship has been growing since October 2019, and she doesn't seem to have been bothered by his engagement.</p>

